Reset Windows 10 (Keep Files Safe)
🔌 1. Insert bootable USB
Plug in your Windows 10 USB
Restart the PC
⌨️ 2. Open Boot Menu

Press repeatedly:

F12 / ESC / F9 / DEL (depends on brand)

Select your USB drive

🪟 3. Windows Setup screen
Select language → Click Next
🛠️ 4. Click Repair
Click “Repair your computer” (bottom-left)
🔄 5. Go to Troubleshoot
Click Troubleshoot
Click Reset this PC
🟢 6. Choose “Keep my files”

👉 Same as Windows 11

✔ Keeps:

Documents
Pictures
Desktop files

❌ Removes:

Apps/programs
Password
⚙️ 7. Choose reinstall
Click Local reinstall (recommended)
▶️ 8. Start reset
Click Reset
PC will restart and begin

⏳ Takes 20–60 minutes

🎉 9. After reset
No password
Files still there
Windows is fresh
